Package net.maswag.falcaun

Class NumericSULMapper

java.lang.Object
net.maswag.falcaun.NumericSULMapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Mapper<String,String,List<Double>,IOSignalPiece<List<Double>>>, Mapper.SynchronousMapper<String,String,List<Double>,IOSignalPiece<List<Double>>>, SULMapper<String,String,List<Double>,IOSignalPiece<List<Double>>>
Direct Known Subclasses:
NumericSULMapperWithSGA
public class NumericSULMapper extends Object implements SULMapper<String,String,List<Double>,IOSignalPiece<List<Double>>>
I/O Mapper between abstract/concrete NumericSUL.

This class provides mapping between abstract string-based inputs/outputs and concrete signal-based inputs/outputs.

Author:
Masaki Waga <masakiwaga@gmail.com>
